se the \\\"Olympic lanes\\\" referring to the 185 kilometres of roads around Paris reserved for delegations, taxis, buses, and journalists - a major disappointment for both the Uber drivers and the company.\", \"from\": 4631, \"to\": 4874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4745, \"end\": 4750, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2433591243168396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Uber drivers\", \"from\": 4640, \"to\": 4652}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"Olympic lanes\", \"from\": 4677, \"to\": 4695}, {\"ngram\": \"the 185 kilometres\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4728}, {\"ngram\": \"roads\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4737}, {\"ngram\": \"delegations\", \"from\": 4764, \"to\": 4775}, {\"ngram\": \"taxis\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4782}, {\"ngram\": \"buses\", \"from\": 4784, \"to\": 4789}, {\"ngram\": \"journalists\", \"from\": 4795, \"to\": 4806}, {\"ngram\": \"a major disappointment\", \"from\": 4809, \"to\": 4831}, {\"ngram\": \"both the Uber drivers\", \"from\": 4836, \"to\": 4857}, {\"ngram\": \"the company\", \"from\": 4862, \"to\": 4873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We really feel a discrimination between ride-hailing apps and taxis,\\\" said Karim Daoud, President of the Union representing ride-hailing drivers in France (AVF).\", \"from\": 4876, \"to\": 5038, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4952, \"end\": 4957, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\", \"score\": 0.9999996790311858, \"rank\": 3.1910073675853713e-07, \"text\": \"Karim\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karim_Wade\"}, {\"begin\": 4982, \"end\": 4987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999999999998181, \"rank\": 1.8716656848560866e-12, 