, \"from\": 5173, \"to\": 5182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Daoud hinted at the possibility of a strike of Uber drivers during the sporting event: \\\"We reserve the right to hold protests.\", \"from\": 5204, \"to\": 5333, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mr Daoud\", \"from\": 5204, \"to\": 5212}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 5223, \"to\": 5238}, {\"ngram\": \"a strike\", \"from\": 5242, \"to\": 5250}, {\"ngram\": \"Uber drivers\", \"from\": 5254, \"to\": 5266}, {\"ngram\": \"the sporting event\", \"from\": 5274, \"to\": 5292}, {\"ngram\": \"the right\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 5324, \"to\": 5332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's still on the agenda but we advocate for some sort of dialogue first.\\\"\", \"from\": 5334, \"to\": 5410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the agenda\", \"from\": 5350, \"to\": 5360}, {\"ngram\": \"some sort\", \"from\": 5381, \"to\": 5390}, {\"ngram\": \"dialogue\", \"from\": 5394, \"to\": 5402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the passenger side,Uberpromises to contain the surge in prices.\", \"from\": 5412, \"to\": 5478, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the passenger side\", \"from\": 5415, \"to\": 5433}, {\"ngram\": \"the surge\", \"from\": 5458, \"to\": 5467}, {\"ngram\": \"prices\", \"from\": 5471, \"to\": 5477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the millions of visitors expected in Paris this summer, the price surge will be limited to \\\"10 to 15%\\\", assured Laureline Serieys, the General Manager of Uber in France.\", \"from\": 5479, \"to\": 5656, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5524, \"end\": 5529, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2433591243168396e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 5599, \"end\": 5608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Val\\u00e9rian_and_Lau